oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Parents' Pride
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Memphis Chamber of Commerce; newsletters; education; Grinner, Edna Lucille; Grinner family; portraits;
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: "Parents' pride in their daughter's accomplishment is evidenced as Mr. and Mrs. Henry Grinner admire the certificate received by Edna Lucille Grinner of Barret's Chapel High School. The honor student will study at Fisk University on a scholarship won for making the highest score on a college entrance examination."
oai_dc:dc.dc:contributor: Gift of Eric Elam (Director of Operations, Greater Memphis Chamber)
